reviews.review_text: Beautiful Matrix I love the sound of this matrix. You feel like you are at the show, the sound has dimension to it. Right from the start, the band is putting off great, positive energy in Alabama>Promised. This version of Loser transports me back in time to a wild west saloon somewhere in the High Plains. The rest of the shows smokes. Check it out!
special guest WOW! great recording. John Belushi took the stage during the encore to duetting U.S Blues!!

Hidden Gem Great show. High energy. The end of Scarlett is simply ferocious. Outstanding!

Thanks for the Matrix as the SBD is sub par. Nice Work.
